The key differences between traveling in Belgium and Democratic Republic of the Congo will affect the Real Cost of traveling. You are able to compare the Real Cost of Traveling from each country in two ways:
1. By transforming the input data into a globally comparable measure that can be used to take into account the differences in travel costs of Basic Information, Your Income and What You Eat by using proportionately the same number of Swiss Francs (ch.).
